      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以核心状态是静止、运动和事故三种？另外我需要加上无障碍支持，给图表加上可访问的标题和描述。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "accTitle",
        "accDescr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，状态就是Still、Moving和Crash。流转关系是：从初始状态先到静止，静止可以变运动，运动可以返回静止，运动也可能变成事故，事故和静止都能到终止状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "state transitions"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，状态和流转关系已经画好了。现在我来定义样式类：静止状态用白色填充；运动状态用斜体字体；事故状态需要特别醒目，用红色背景、白色粗体字，加上黄色边框。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "classDef notMoving",
        "classDef movement",
        "classDef badBadEvent",
        "fill:white",
        "font-style:italic",
        "fill:#f00",
        "font-weight:bold",
        "stroke:yellow"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "事故状态的样式很好，很醒目。应用样式吧：静止用notMoving类，运动和事故都用movement类，事故还要加上badBadEvent类。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "class Still notMoving",
        "class Moving, Crash movement",
        "class Crash badBadEvent"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，我注意到您说\"运动和事故都用movement类\"，但事故状态已经用了badBadEvent，再叠加movement类的斜体会不会冲突？还有您提到\"事故还要加上badBadEvent类\"，但前面已经说了，我确认一下：Moving和Crash都用movement，只有Crash额外加badBadEvent对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "class Moving, Crash movement",
        "class Crash badBadEvent",
        "style conflict"
